  <!-- Process Section -->
  <ProcessSection 
    serviceType="invoice-finance"
    title="Getting Invoice Finance is Straightforward"
    description="Our streamlined process gets you the cash flow you need quickly and efficiently."
    disclaimer="Invoice finance terms and availability subject to credit assessment and invoice quality. Protection against bad debt may apply additional criteria."
  />

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 font-['Instrument_Sans'] text-[#1C2C3B]">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white shadow-md">
            <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex justify-between items-center faq-toggle">
              <span class="font-semibold text-[#1C2C3B]">What types of invoices qualify for invoice finance?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4">
              <p class="text-gray-600">Generally, invoices from creditworthy commercial customers with payment terms of 30-90 days qualify. The lender will assess each customer's creditworthiness and payment history to determine eligibility.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white shadow-md">
            <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex justify-between items-center faq-toggle">
              <span class="font-semibold text-[#1C2C3B]">How much can I access through invoice finance?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4">
              <p class="text-gray-600">Up to 100% of the invoice value is advanced immediately, with the balance (minus fees) paid when your business customer settles the invoice. Facilities can range from $50,000 to several million dollars depending on your invoice volumes and can scale with the growth of your business.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white shadow-md">
            <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex justify-between items-center faq-toggle">
              <span class="font-semibold text-[#1C2C3B]">What are the costs of invoice finance?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4">
              <p class="text-gray-600">Costs typically include a factoring fee (percentage of invoice value) and may include service fees. Rates vary based on industry, customer quality, and invoice volumes. We'll provide a clear fee structure before you commit.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white shadow-md">
            <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex justify-between items-center faq-toggle">
              <span class="font-semibold text-[#1C2C3B]">Do my customers know about the invoice finance arrangement?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4">
              <p class="text-gray-600">This depends on the arrangement. With disclosed factoring, customers are notified and pay directly to the factoring company. With confidential invoice finance, customers may not be aware of the arrangement and continue paying to you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white shadow-md">
            <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex justify-between items-center faq-toggle">
              <span class="font-semibold text-[#1C2C3B]">How quickly can I access funds?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4">
              <p class="text-gray-600">Once your facility is established and invoices are submitted and approved, funds are typically available within 24 hours. Initial setup may take 5-7 business days depending on documentation requirements.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Newsletter CTA Section -->
  <NewsLetter />
